# Service-account / credential material — NEVER commit. The GCIP import script
# (scripts/migration/import-users-to-gcip.js) and the Firebase Hosting CD
# (.github/workflows/deploy-frontend-firebase.yml) instruct operators to supply a
# Firebase Admin / deployer SA JSON; these patterns make that promise real so a
# stray `git add .` cannot stage a live GCP credential.
*-admin.json
service-account*.json
serviceAccount*.json
*-sa.json
firebase-debug.log
.firebase/

zk/tmp/
zk/input/
zk/circomlib/
zk/build/circuit_0000.zkey
